-- Putin’s Rights Panel May Draw in Opposition, Vedomosti Reports
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-06-22T04:58:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/putin-s-rights-panel-may-draw-in-opposition-vedomosti-reports.html
Leonid Parfyonov, a TV presenter and
co-founder of the Voters League, an independent election
watchdog, and Boris Akunin, a popular detective novelist who led
thousands on a Moscow protest walk in May, are among the
candidates for  Russia ’s Presidential Human Rights Council,
 Vedomosti  reported.  --
